title: Matt Miller, professional photographer & Most Precious Blood
itunes:title: Matt Miller, professional photographer & Most Precious Blood
description:
Matt Miller is my favorite photographer around right now and I was really excited that not only was he a fan of the podcast, but that he wanted to be a guest on the show. He came over to my house and we discussed skateboarding, the art of photography and finding what you are passionate about. Visit patreon.com/xpurposex for our fundraising campaign! 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
